        "heading": "1. Background; 5. Recommendations",
        "locator": "pages 8–12",
        "evidence_summary": "Defines dermatophyte subtypes but focuses on tinea pedis, including itch, scale, fissures, maceration, erythema, vesicles, ulcers, and foot distribution."
